data.content: What trace elements are included in Garden Fertiliser?

The Garden Fertiliser includes Sodium Molybdate and Sodium Borate as part of its composition. These trace elements, along with others not specifically mentioned, contribute to the comprehensive soil health and overall plant growth benefits the product offers.
